FX:Rigs
As a user I want to look at other guitarists effects rigs and be able to comment on their setup.
As a user I want to upload my own effects rig and provide information to other guitarists about my setup.
As a user I want to see popular rig setups from other users and famous guitarists.
As a user I want to write/read a review individual effects pedals in a rig and have a description of settings.
As a user I want to search for effects pedals/rigs by musical genre.
As a user I want to search for effects pedals by pedal type.
As a user I want to listen to / upload sound clips of particular effects pedal settings.


Relationships


Users:
has many rigs
has and belongs to many pedals
has many favourites

Rigs: 
belongs to user
has and belongs to many pedals
belongs to genre
has many favourites

Pedals: 
has and belongs to many rigs
has and belongs to many users

Genres:
has many rigs

Favourites:
belongs to user
belongs to rig
  